Package: optimalppp
Type: Package
Version: 0.0.0.1
Title: Optimal Project Prioritization Protocol
Description: Prioritize conservation projects for funding under limited
    budgets. Although solutions can be identified using heuristic algorithms,
    to identify optimal solutions the 'Gurobi' optimizer will need to be
    installed (available from <https://www.gurobi.com>).
